{"tid":1840454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［生化危機保衛戰］（同行動post有關，請推依個post)一人至少諗+帶一樣防身武器","createTime":"2020-01-24T22:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T03:20:11.000Z","uid":225828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7bd8b251c7cbe7444a9da7f71a9d845ef7283157","tid":1840454,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T22:57:35.000Z","msg":"大家睇過人玩或者玩過生化危機嘅都知<br />\n赤手空拳係冇可能打得贏喪屍(你唔係一拳超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">係一定要有武器先可以打得死班喪屍怪物！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n石器時代嘅時候人類可以打得贏野獸係靠石器同火器<br />\n換句話講即係靠武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都睇過扯口罩嗰段片，武漢嗰啲人癲起上嚟係真係唔係人咁品，隨時扮喪屍咬鳩你都不為過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗去包圍GAO 鐵站之外<br />\n<br />\n對付喪屍不得不準備一啲防身武器<br />\n<br />\n用刀嗰啲太殘忍因為大家都唔係殺人狂魔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>但係如果好似之前同犬隻對陣嘅時候掉野遠攻班喪屍呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n要記住其實如果佢哋攻入嚟我哋真係會命仔玩完<br />\n<br />\n已經唔係政唔政治一回事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係俾佢成班喪屍衝入嚟香港一定淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">保衞香港嘅唔係靠政府<br />\n唔係靠犬隻<br />\n更加唔係靠蝙蝠俠<br />\n<br />\n係靠熱愛香港嘅一眾香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n當啲喪屍想係Gao鐵上面沖過嚟香港睇霸王醫生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋要做嘅就係要掉到佢驚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n掉到佢退！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n掉到佢哋懷疑人生！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n要清楚比到個訊息佢哋：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>就算落嚟香港都唔會幫到佢哋嘅病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n逼佢地返返去自己個狗竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n逼支那政府自己拆返掂壇嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港話晒都係我哋自己地頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇理由自己地頭都比人哋恰鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你覺得佢都係人嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n諗下佢哋點樣虐待啲寵物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗下佢哋變態到連人類BB都食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗下佢哋點樣恩將仇報對所有幫過佢嘅人包括醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你就知道佢哋已經唔係人係喪屍<br />\n<br />\n而如果到而家一刻都唔攞起自己嘅武器去保護自己嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n換來嘅結果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只會係疫症會喺香港社區大爆發<br />\n<br />\n會造成大量嘅香港人死亡<br />\n<br />\n甚至係你地嘅親人同埋最愛嘅人都會受到傷害</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔通你真係忍心見到你哋心愛嘅人要遭受到武漢人嘅結果咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">去圍GAO 鐵嘅時候,帶定幾罐罐裝雀巢咖啡又好、罐裝可口可樂又好、甚至係叔一燒都好<br />\n我哋嘅目的好簡單：<br />\n至少係依段時間要打到班喪屍唔敢再衝落嚟香港！<br />\n要逼到香港政府封關！<br />\n要令到香港呢個地方唔好再因為肺炎造成不必要傷亡</span><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999, 好耐冇打篇咁長嘅文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝香港同香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">願平安歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>香港人，起嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"faa8ac8382c2acf167029e11f82929bdd7e85517","tid":1840454,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T22:58:25.000Z","msg":"準備戰爭"},{"pid":"51b349d44107700508b942544c316c41a190bfd4","tid":1840454,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:15:30.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"4ea6a64baadf6d90c8fac742dc2fc099b2c6c814","tid":1840454,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:15:42.000Z","msg":"1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e358265c610b2e41ddf260212b1257a6996b239","tid":1840454,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:15:54.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a17f2b7225be5b4462e0dd6ebced7844770546","tid":1840454,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:16:05.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365531e2790f020c090282b6ca91a1210cbbc2da","tid":1840454,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:16:19.000Z","msg":"4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e33bff4cbf41eac1faa9f3036bd0db8b3cdb895","tid":1840454,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:16:30.000Z","msg":"5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a9d63dfc331a2a18fc112e1814ac6fa0bfab51","tid":1840454,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:16:42.000Z","msg":"6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f4d7ede2435c1ed27fd19f1d95327392e79d7c","tid":1840454,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T23:16:55.000Z","msg":"7/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi